name: Generative Calendar — Reservation ticket
description:
Collecting an edition of this ticket allows you to reserve a date of choice of the Generative Calendar collection by Andreas Rau (https://objkt.com/collection/KT1GH7Psn9q7Jkrr88jgUiniN4LGDWrrg15n).

You will receive one of 365 unique variations of the same generative algorithm (1/1 of 365). First come, first served.

Check the availability and place your reservation for a date of your choice via andreasrau.eu/generativecalendar. The reserved token will be airdropped into your wallet on the respective date.

Original artwork by Andreas Rau · Oslo, 2022
